name: OpenOptionsPDF

properties.name: typename
properties.description: The class name of the object.

properties.name: pageToOpen
properties.description: What page should be used when opening a multipage document (default: 1)

properties.name: pDFCropToBox
properties.description: What box should be used when placing a multipage document (default: PDF media box)

properties.name: pageRangeToOpen
properties.description: Range of pages when opening a multipage document [possible values: 'all', range(for example: '1,2,3-5,8')]

properties.name: placeAsLinks
properties.description: Import PDF pages as links for optimal performance (default: true for PageRangeToOpen=all; false otherwise)

description: Options which may be supplied when opening a PDF file.
